# {{.ProjectName}}

A production-ready Go REST API built with security and observability best practices.

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Start all services (API, PostgreSQL, Redis)
make up

# Check if the API is running
curl http://localhost:8080/health/ready

# View logs
make logs

# Stop all services
make down
```

## 📋 Features

- ✅ **Fiber HTTP Server** - High-performance web framework
- ✅ **Health Checks** - Kubernetes-ready liveness and readiness probes
- ✅ **Structured Logging** - Request correlation with unique IDs
- ✅ **Graceful Shutdown** - Safe termination with connection draining
- ✅ **Security Headers** - HSTS, CSP, X-Frame-Options, and more
- ✅ **PostgreSQL** - Production-grade relational database
- ✅ **Redis** - High-performance caching layer
- ✅ **Docker Compose** - Zero-config local development
- ✅ **Environment Config** - Type-safe configuration management

